{"tid":909170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊藝媛淫照被非法上載 24歲色情網負責人被捕","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T11:55:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e50d36e1d995bb63960b78c63e985924c2592e3c","tid":909170,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181120/large/1542692011_f8a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181120%2Flarge%2F1542692011_f8a7.jpg&h=c04f4281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國網上早前流出逾200名女性模特兒嘅不雅照，當中網紅楊藝媛嘅淫照亦包括在內，警方接獲報案後調查事件。隨後楊藝媛含淚拍片，自爆淫照係佢喺大前年應徵模特兒期間拍攝，但拍攝當時就遭到性騷擾，事件引起熱議。楊藝媛起訴影樓攝影師一案於今年9月開審。<br />\n<br />\n據首爾地方警察廳網絡搜查隊表示，近日以違反性暴力犯罪條例，拘捕咗非法營運該色情網站嘅24歲網站負責人，而將淫照上載到網站嘅35歲獸醫等合共86人，亦一同被警方立案起訴。警方續指眾人涉嫌於去年9月至上月，透過美國伺服器上載照片到該色情網站，合共獲得8.3萬港元廣告費。"},{"pid":"b93137e63e229dc529ed4823c3bd4a94a250baf8","tid":909170,"uid":35699,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"非法上載到連登仔接觸唔到o既地方"},{"pid":"6fa91927c81f7b8efa28401e5dca241bbbc79583","tid":909170,"uid":179266,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"數撚到口乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209cd9b5349b2fc370e711338d8b18a3b9e40aff","tid":909170,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"召喚冰山圖"},{"pid":"209112742a7284c1e86f559c65e62da57370b7f5","tid":909170,"uid":57871,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"流出？瘋傳？又係冇連燈份"},{"pid":"17ba4210c746f3ff1560d860fc5a7b4cbc701a2f","tid":909170,"uid":48667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"又upload 左去啲全世界都睇到既地方<br />\n係得連登仔睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afabb516fb99c964dbace580ae25a5d3556861e